{"tid":1180331,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"守口如瓶","createTime":"2019-05-31T18:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T18:23:07.000Z","uid":9233,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"787b18a9b9f75cc3c3c1cb2f4135f65d3219a9ba","tid":1180331,"uid":9233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:13:06.000Z","msg":"長年在駐守縱未夠運氣開口<br />\n暗中傾慕你也是我有的自由<br />\n連眉目也生銹<br />\n如忘掉了色誘<br />\n才能橫越幾多春和秋<br />\n<br />\n瓶內沒有酒你別引導我失守<br />\n留白這一塊我們友誼更永久<br />\n情誼若已足夠<br />\n眉目亦可參透<br />\n情懷還是講不出來更深厚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近同一個識左幾年既朋友單獨出多左街<br />\n好似對佢產生左好感<br />\n<br />\n但係我諗佢應該只係當我係朋友<br />\n甚至feel到我對佢有好感開始對我有啲冷淡<br />\n唔想無左呢個朋友<br />\n好想平常心咁對佢但係又會忍唔住去留意佢關心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e704748649f1a6c8985726b6cf12bca707289c3","tid":1180331,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:14:14.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"6ad4239f5f43c3fb09f9012ed2e5b3a67a46a982","tid":1180331,"uid":9233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e704748649f1a6c8985726b6cf12bca707289c3","tid":1180331,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:14:14.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:18:26.000Z","msg":"真係渣<br />\n知道自己無乜機會都要鍾個頭落去"},{"pid":"78591d6f370d2ae3a1124eb08a1f5a1144bd42ef","tid":1180331,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ad4239f5f43c3fb09f9012ed2e5b3a67a46a982","tid":1180331,"uid":9233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e704748649f1a6c8985726b6cf12bca707289c3","tid":1180331,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:14:14.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:18:26.000Z","msg":"真係渣<br />\n知道自己無乜機會都要鍾個頭落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31